**v1 spec:**

```json
{
  "initiators": [
    {
      "type": "web"
    }
  ],
  "tasks": [
    {
      "type": "multiply",
      "params": {
        "times": 100
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "custombridge"
    }
  ]
}
